---
title: Enjoy all the articles
layout: page
permalink: /posts/
seo:
  robots: noindex
---

<div class="not-prose mt-10 space-y-16 pt-10 sm:mt-16 sm:pt-16">
  {%- for post in collections.allPosts | reverse -%}
    <article class="flex max-w-xl flex-col items-start justify-between">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-x-4 text-xs">
        {% if post.data.date %}
          <time datetime="{{ post.data.date }}">{{ post.data.date | datefmt }}</time>
        {% else %}
          <time datetime="{{ page.date }}">{{ page.date | datefmt }}</time>
        {% endif %}

        {% if post.data.scheduled %}
          <p class="relative z-10 rounded-full bg-yellow-100 px-3 py-1.5 font-medium text-yellow-700 hover: hover:bg-yellow-200">Scheduled</p>
        {% endif %}

        {% if post.data.draft %}
          <p class="relative z-10 rounded-full bg-red-100 px-3 py-1.5 font-medium text-red-700 hover: hover:bg-red-200">Draft</p>
        {% endif %}

        {% for tag in post.data.tags %}
          <a href="/category/{{ tag | slugify }}/" class="relative z-10 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-violet-50 via-purple-100 to-fuchsia-200 px-3 py-1.5 font-medium text-purple-800 hover:text-purple-950 hover:from-violet-200 hover:via-purple-300 hover:to-fuchsia-400 focus:text-purple-100 focus:from-violet-400 focus:via-purple-500 focus:to-fuchsia-600">{{ tag }}</a>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
      <div class="group relative">
        <h3 class="mt-3 text-lg font-semibold leading-6 text-slate-900 group-hover:text-slate-600">
          <a href="{{ post.url }}">
            <span class="absolute inset-0"></span>{{ post.data.title }}</a>
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-5 line-clamp-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600">Illo sint voluptas. Error voluptates culpa eligendi. Hic vel totam vitae illo. Non aliquid explicabo necessitatibus unde. Sed exercitationem placeat consectetur nulla deserunt vel iusto corrupti dicta laboris incididunt.</p>
      </div>
    </article>
  {%- endfor -%}
</div>
<div class="prose mt-16">
  <p>See <a href="/category/">all categories</a>.</p>
</div>